sentences.en: Most SOA/Middleware will utilize the following technologies: IBM WebSphere; MQ Series, DB2, Tivoli, and Rational,TIBCO Product Suite, Rendezvous; Oracle/BEA AquaLogic, WebLogic, Tuxedo, Fusion; Microsoft.NET, BizTalk.
sentences.vi: Phần lớn SOA/Middleware sẽ dùng các công nghệ sau: IBM WebSphere; MQ Series, DB2, Tivoli, và Rational,TIBCO Product Suite, Rendezvous; Oracle/BEA AquaLogic, WebLogic, Tuxedo, Fusion; Microsoft.NET, BizTalk.
